    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classMR_1_1PickPointManager" kindref="compound">PickPointManager</ref> allows the user to pick/move/delete several ordered points on one or more visual objects; mouse events and public methods automatically add history actions for reverting (if enabled) </para>
